\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 [C2.1]\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94Why then.\u8221\'94 You ask. He motions for you to follow. You follow.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 [C2.2.1]\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94Why then.\u8221\'94 You ask. He motions for you to follow. You don\u8217\'92t trust him in any way. \u8220\'93What? I\u8217\'92m not going with you.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 [C2.2.2]Whatever they\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92re planning maybe you can stop it right here and now. You thumb the flick knife in your pocket.}
